tachments, explosives and equipment.\n\n\u2022 Take note of simulated wind and target distance with the wind meter and spotter scope. Calculate physics-based bullet drop and time-to-hit to improve your accuracy.\n\n\u2022 Use stealth to sneak up behind enemies with a silent knife kill. Or go head-to-head against enemies that will take cover and attempt to flank your position.\n\n\u2022 Randomized Enemy positions and doors, making each play-through an unknown challenge.\n\n\u2022 Non-linear maps give players an endless variety in how they choose to infiltrate and complete missions. Enter buildings through doors, climb ladders to reach rooftops, or climb through windows. The choice is yours.\n\nTactical Assault VR is currently an Early Access release and is updated regularly.", "short_description": "Tactical MilSim CQB (Close Quarters Battles) in Virtual Reality"}]}, "developer_name": "Twisted Barrel Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://twistedbarrelgames.wixsite.com/tactical-assault-vr/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Twisted Barrel Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://twistedbarrelgames.wixsite.com/tactical-assault-vr", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "3744040075834813"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "SHOOTER"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GAMEPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "707998687088613"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 4, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "588737080163342"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1357851021858876"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "828997436054349"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1773876819610591"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1357851021858876"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1734372000, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "588737080163342"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8986478851409833", "version": "0.8.5"}, "id": "1336107373548228", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5190911237633299", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8986478851409833"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1336107373548228"}]}, "change_log": "Tactical Assault VR v0.8.5 Breaking Whisper\n\u2022 Added Breaking Whisper Mission\n\u2022 Added Shootout mode to multiplayer coop map selection\n\u2022 Added Map Drawing/Planning to Training Lobbies and Main Menu (Engineered by Justin P. Barnett)\n\u2022 Added AK105 Rifle (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added M16 Classic Rifle w/ burst fire (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added VEPR12 Primary Shotgun (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added M4 Entry Primary Shotgun (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added 590 Mariner Primary Shotgun (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added 590A1 Primary Shotgun (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added MICH Low helmets to Avatar Customization (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added FM12 gas mask to avatar customization (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added Boonie Camo to Avatar Customization\n\u2022 Added Press (War Correspondent) Avatar in Gender Selection. You can now identify as PRESS\n\u2022 Added \"Antonio Smith\" to head selection (Eduardo's brother)\n\u2022 Added Grenade Kill scoring\n\u2022 Added Friendly Fire toggle in multiplayer coop lobbies\n\u2022 Added additional Vest speed options to Avatar Customization\n\u2022 Updated Spotter Scope to Moskito style scope (Modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Updated Mission Selection UI\n\u2022 Normal difficulty enemies now carry random weapons between M4A1 and AKM\n\u2022 Added Enemy Strafing when firing\n\u2022 Enemies will be alerted if they pass by a dead enemy body\n\u2022 Increased enemy alertness for passing bullets and bullet impacts\n\u2022 Removed enemy weapon hitboxes. Increased enemy reaction time for difficulty balance\n\u2022 Updated Enemy Ai logic and animation transitions\n\u2022 Updated: Hostages are now enemy targets after triggering them to follow\n\u2022 Significantly lowered hostage health. Dead hostage = mission failure\n\u2022 Hostages no longer take commands from downed/dead players\n\u2022 Updated singleplayer sandbox to use multiplayer sandbox with room randomizer\n\u2022 Added night-time sandbox and room randomizer to singleplayer\n\u2022 Added bomb defusal to sandbox and room randomizer\n\u2022 Fixed 2-handed weapon haptics when firing\n\u2022 Fixed VGMod3 and Hand Stop grip holstering rifles when the primary grip is released\n\u2022 Fixed Vest speed resetting\n\u2022 Return of PvP Night Time maps\n\u2022 Updated various weapon sound fx\n\u2022 Various under-the-hood improvements and changes\n\u2022 (Quest) Added Weapon Fire smoke\n\nKnown Issues:\n\u2022 Multiplayer Breaking Whisper boat infiltration. Avatars can and will get stacked on top of each other\n\u2022 Shotgun shells cannot be placed back into pouches after they have been taken from a pouch\n\u2022 SPAS currently only has pump-action and cannot be switched to semi-auto\n", "created_date": 1734385203, "id": "8986478851409833", "version": "0.8.5", "version_code": 323, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8986477981409920"}, "asset_